{"type":"message","id":"17cec9fc","parentId":"19ffcda8","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:05:00.378Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d Context Monitor] powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\miliger-context-manager\\scripts\\context-monitor.ps1\nCurrent time: Thursday, March 19th, 2026 — 19:05 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-19 11:05 UTC"}],"timestamp":1773918300377}}
{"type":"message","id":"5b287dcd","parentId":"17cec9fc","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:05:06.744Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is sending a heartbeat/context monitor cron event. Let me check the heartbeat script and follow its instructions.","thinkingSignature":"632f06eb62e24b5e5d19cb1553609d5cb8122d6ec7aaa648725bd5c55072c1a8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8vbabsov9gxk_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\HEARTBEAT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8vbabsov9gxk_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\skills\\miliger-context-manager\\scripts\\context-monitor.ps1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":161,"output":106,"cacheRead":37011,"cacheWrite":102,"totalTokens":37380,"cost":{"input":0.00006440000000000001,"output":0.00015900000000000002,"cacheRead":0.00148044,"cacheWrite":0.0000153,"total":0.0017191399999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773918300378}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf0b31ae","parentId":"5b287dcd","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:05:06.754Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8vbabsov9gxk_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n# Keep this file empty (or with only comments) to skip heartbeat API calls.\n\n# Add tasks below when you want the agent to check something periodically.\n\n## Context Manager Check\n\n- Run session_status to check current context usage\n- If context > 60%, consider saving memory and preparing for session switch\n- Check ~/proactivity/session-state.md for active tasks\n- Update ~/proactivity/memory/working-buffer.md if needed\n\n## Self-Improving Check\n\n- Read ./skills/self-improving/heartbeat-rules.md\n- Use ~/self-improving/heartbeat-state.md for last-run markers and action notes\n- If no file inside ~/self-improving/ changed since the last reviewed change, return HEARTBEAT_OK\n\n## Proactivity Check\n\n- Read ~/proactivity/heartbeat.md\n- Re-check active blockers, promised follow-ups, stale work, and missing decisions\n- Ask what useful check-in or next move would help right now\n- Message the user only when something changed or needs a decision\n- Update ~/proactivity/session-state.md after meaningful follow-through\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773918306752}}
{"type":"message","id":"10963af6","parentId":"bf0b31ae","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:05:06.756Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8vbabsov9gxk_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Context Monitor for Windows\n# Monitors OpenClaw session context usage and alerts when threshold is reached\n\nparam(\n    [int]$Threshold = 60,\n    [string]$LogDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\logs\",\n    [string]$LogFile = \"$LogDir\\context-monitor.log\"\n)\n\n# Ensure log directory exists\nif (!(Test-Path $LogDir)) {\n    New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $LogDir -Force | Out-Null\n}\n\nfunction Write-Log($Message) {\n    $timestamp = Get-Date -Format \"yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss\"\n    \"$timestamp - $Message\" | Out-File -Append -FilePath $LogFile\n    Write-Host \"$timestamp - $Message\"\n}\n\n# Get session list to check context usage\ntry {\n    # Use .NET Process to properly separate stdout and stderr\n    $psi = New-Object System.Diagnostics.ProcessStartInfo\n    $psi.FileName = \"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\openclaw.cmd\"\n    $psi.Arguments = \"sessions --json\"\n    $psi.RedirectStandardOutput = $true\n    $psi.RedirectStandardError = $true\n    $psi.UseShellExecute = $false\n    $psi.CreateNoWindow = $true\n    \n    $process = New-Object System.Diagnostics.Process\n    $process.StartInfo = $psi\n    $process.Start() | Out-Null\n    \n    $stdout = $process.StandardOutput.ReadToEnd()\n    $stderr = $process.StandardError.ReadToEnd()\n    $process.WaitForExit()\n    \n    if ($stdout) {\n        # Extract JSON from stdout (find content between first { and last })\n        $jsonStart = $stdout.IndexOf('{')\n        $jsonEnd = $stdout.LastIndexOf('}')\n        \n        if ($jsonStart -ge 0 -and $jsonEnd -gt $jsonStart) {\n            $jsonContent = $stdout.Substring($jsonStart, $jsonEnd - $jsonStart + 1)\n            $data = $jsonContent | ConvertFrom-Json -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n            \n            if ($data -and $data.sessions) {\n                # Find main session\n                $mainSession = $data.sessions | Where-Object { $_.key -eq 'agent:main:main' } | Select-Object -First 1\n                \n                if ($mainSession -and $mainSession.totalTokens -and $mainSession.contextTokens) {\n                    $used = $mainSession.totalTokens\n                    $total = $mainSession.contextTokens\n                    $usage = [math]::Round(($used / $total) * 100)\n                    \n                    Write-Log \"Context usage: ${usage}% (${used}/${total} tokens)\"\n                    \n                    if ($usage -ge $Threshold) {\n                        Write-Log \"WARNING: Context usage ${usage}% exceeds threshold ${Threshold}%\"\n                        \n                        # Check memory files\n                        $memoryDir = \"$env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\"\n                        $memoryLite = \"$memoryDir\\MEMORY-LITE.md\"\n                        \n                        if (Test-Path $memoryLite) {\n                            $content = Get-Content $memoryLite -Raw -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n                            $wordCount = ($content -split '\\s+').Count\n                            Write-Log \"MEMORY-LITE.md: $wordCount words\"\n                        }\n                        \n                        Write-Log \"ALERT: Consider starting a new session to reset context\"\n                    } else {\n                        Write-Log \"Context usage normal: ${usage}%\"\n                    }\n                } else {\n                    Write-Log \"Main session found but no token info available\"\n                }\n            } else {\n                Write-Log \"No sessions data found in JSON\"\n            }\n        } else {\n            Write-Log \"Could not find JSON content in output\"\n        }\n    } else {\n        Write-Log \"No output from sessions command\"\n    }\n} catch {\n    Write-Log \"Error checking context: $_\"\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773918306754}}
{"type":"message","id":"61e97aec","parentId":"10963af6","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:05:10.550Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The heartbeat script checks context usage and logs it. Let me also check the session status and other relevant files as per HEARTBEAT.md.","thinkingSignature":"3c55cac410ff407d6d32ff79d3d8fd26258c2701f0da9736265aaa6f510fa6ac"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dql1sbjd56iy_1","name":"session_status","arguments":{}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dql1sbjd56iy_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\proactivity\\heartbeat.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dql1sbjd56iy_3","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\proactivity\\session-state.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1449,"output":116,"cacheRead":37011,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38576,"cost":{"input":0.0005796000000000001,"output":0.000174,"cacheRead":0.00148044,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00223404}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773918306756}}
{"type":"message","id":"efb36f1b","parentId":"61e97aec","timestamp":"2026-03-19T11:05:10.889Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dql1sbjd56iy_1","toolName":"session_status","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a)\n🕒 Time: Thursday, March 19th, 2026 — 19:05 (Asia/Shanghai)\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 · 🔑 api-key (minimax:cn)\n🧮 Tokens: 11k in / 1.7k out · 💵 Cost: $0.0068\n🗄️ Cache: 96% hit · 296k cached, 102 new\n📚 Context: 41k/200k (21%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n📊 Usage: 5h 46% left ⏱54m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d • updated just now\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"}],"details":{"ok":true,"sessionKey":"agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d","changedModel":false,"statusText":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.13 (61d171a)\n🕒 Time: Thursday, March 19th, 2026 — 19:05 (Asia/Shanghai)\n🧠 Model: minimax/MiniMax-M2.7 · 🔑 api-key (minimax:cn)\n🧮 Tokens: 11k in / 1.7k out · 💵 Cost: $0.0068\n🗄️ Cache: 96% hit · 296k cached, 102 new\n📚 Context: 41k/200k (21%) · 🧹 Compactions: 0\n📊 Usage: 5h 46% left ⏱54m\n🧵 Session: agent:main:cron:696799cb-400f-4ac4-9393-6c861584965d • updated just now\n⚙️ Runtime: direct · Think: off · elevated\n🪢 Queue: collect (depth 0)"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773918310887}}
